            <a href="/docs/start-here" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline">Customer Docs</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/scottgal/stylobot/blob/main/docs/README.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline">GitHub Docs</a>
